General.Name: Sunsuria Bhd
General.Description: Sunsuria Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the development of properties in Malaysia. It operates through Property Development, Construction, Healthcare, and Investment Holding and Others segments. The company develops commercial, industrial, and residential properties; undertakes construction activities; and provides education, parking, service management, landscape and nursery, and IT and management services. It is also involved in the trading of pharmaceutical and medical goods, as well as healthcare related products; and operation of integrated healthcare center, as well as automobile related, food and beverage, factoring, and restaurants proprietor businesses. The company was formerly known as Malaysia Aica Berhad and changed its name to Sunsuria Berhad in May 2014. Sunsuria Berhad was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
